  automatic FDC switch on drive select via control register bits 6:5
- `emulator_t`: added `microdisc_t`, `sedoric_disk_t* disks[4]`, `has_microdisc`
- `io_read_callback`/`io_write_callback`: route $0310-$031F to Microdisc
